  "parent_catalog_id": "activity",
  "purpose": "A text message (SMS or messaging-app message) sent or received as part of a relationship. A subclass of Activity that adds messaging-specific delta attributes: from / to phone numbers, body text, direction, delivery status, optional message-platform identifier (SMS, WhatsApp, iMessage, Signal).",
